last_episode_to_air.name: Julian #1
last_episode_to_air.overview: Julian is web series about coming out. It was produced as a low budget project by teenagers and tweens from the lgbt youth group "anyway" in Cologne (Germany). The entire series was produced as a volunteer work. A lot of teenagers in German speaking countries watched the series. With English subtitles it will now reach an international audience. The media project queerblick from Germany thanks the team of "Julian" and the "anyway" for its trust to let us present the series in English

name: Julian
overview: Julian is a teen like any other. He drinks beer, has a never ending probelm with his parents and dates a girl. But one day he is attracted by somebody else.
